The paper discusses interference alignment in distributed antenna systems, which involves topics related to information theory (cs.IT), network infrastructure (cs.NI), system design and control (cs.SY), multimedia systems (cs.MM), and communication engineering (cs.CE). The paper specifically focuses on the feasibility and performance of interference alignment in distributed antenna systems, which suggests that it is likely to fall under these sub-categories.
